org.eclipse.papyrus.robotml.deployment.listener

Interface CopyListener


  • public interface CopyListener
    Interface for listeners that are notified for the addition of a classifier via copy
    See Also:
    com.cea.ec3m.gentools.core.transformations.Copy

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject copyEObject(Copy copy, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject sourceEObj)
      Is called for each EObject that is copied.

    • Method Detail

      • copyEObject

        org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject copyEObject(Copy copy,
                                          org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject sourceEObj)
        Is called for each EObject that is copied. If it returns null, the indicated object should not be copied. If it returns a different object than the passed EObject, this object is used (the returned object of the first listener is used).
        Parameters:
        sourceEObj - the added classifier
